Reality TV star, Tochukwu Okechukwu popularly known as Tochi has proposed to his US-based girlfriend, Chioma. The former BBNaija contestant shared the romantic video on his Instagram page where he’s seen with his girlfriend in a public place as he goes down on one knee, reached into his pocket for a beautiful diamond ring and proposed to her. Amidst cheers and performance of Chike’s track, “Running to You” by the live band, she accepted the proposal.   Why I sent Sandra Iheuwa packing five months after wedding,…     Banky W: I was rich but felt empty, struggled with…     Mercy Eke: I dreamt I was a soul-winner for God   He slipped the ring onto her finger, stood up, hugged and begun spraying her with N200 mint notes to the astonishment of his fiancée alongside some others. - Advertisement - Afterward, they hugged again and sealed the proposal with a passionate kiss. The 29-year-old captioned the clip; “To-chi 2022 loaded —— @beautiifulchii let’s go on this journey together!” “Ladies and Gentlemen we have a wedding to plan.”